A JSON array of objects with user details for which the metadata objects should be considered from the repository If you specify ID or name of user and set the type parameter to USER, the API returns metadata objects associated with the user If you specify ID or name of user group and set the type parameter to USER_GROUP, the API returns metadata objects for all the users mapped to the specified user group. If the id or name parameter is not defined, but the type attribute is set to USER or USER_GROUP, then the API will not return and response.
